xmlElements
Class reversegeocode

java.lang.Object
  xmlElements.reversegeocode

public class reversegeocode
extends java.lang.Object

MARSHALL TYPE FROM NOMINATIM API. reversegeocode is the Java class which combines the hierarchy developped in the Addressparts class with a field named "result" used in the unmarshalling in the GeoScalePath class.

1.0 30/01/2014
Author:
